## 1. Product Overview

### 1.1 Product Vision
Create a unified, branded insurance back office platform that consolidates multiple third-party systems into a single, intuitive interface, empowering agents to efficiently manage their business while providing Valor Financial Specialists with comprehensive visibility into organizational performance.

### 1.2 Product Goals
- **Unification:** Single access point for all agent operations
- **Efficiency:** Reduce time spent on administrative tasks by 40%
- **Visibility:** Real-time production tracking and analytics
- **Scalability:** Support 10x growth without platform changes
- **Brand Control:** Consistent Valor Financial Specialists experience

### 1.3 Problem Statement
Insurance agents currently navigate 5+ disparate systems with separate logins, inconsistent interfaces, and disconnected workflows. This fragmentation leads to:
- Lost productivity (average 2 hours/day navigating systems)
- Missed business opportunities
- Poor visibility into performance metrics
- Inconsistent user experience
- Limited organizational control

### 1.4 Solution Overview
A modern web platform that aggregates and streamlines access to all essential insurance operations tools, providing:
- Single Sign-On across all integrated systems
- Unified dashboard with real-time metrics
- Streamlined workflows for common tasks
- Hierarchical visibility and permissions
- Integrated training and support resources

